{"tid":2142855,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台電視] 看見溫度 逢星期四 20:00","createTime":"2020-08-06T17:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T12:36:33.000Z","uid":86449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f1df7346eaa06ea6844f3ee4721beb64dc3b6fa","tid":2142855,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"第二集講香港戰地記者<br />\n無人開 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n生死過後<br />\n童纓瑩（Nicole Tung）是一名攝影記者，多年來報道中東地區利比亞及敍利亞等地的戰火新聞。Nicole在香港出生，於美國紐約大學新聞及歷史系畢業後，以自由身為《紐約時報》等國際報章及雜誌工作。<br />\n<br />\nNicole認為，拍攝一張充滿戲劇效果的戰爭相片並不困難，但更重要的是用相片呈現戰爭對平民百姓生活的影響，以及人們如何在戰火中爭扎求存。<br />\n<br />\n女性的身份也讓Nicole 更容易接觸和理解女性議題，影片記錄了她拍攝ISIS受害者成立的女子軍隊的歷程。<br />\n<br />\n作為戰地記者，親眼目睹生離死別早已不是新鮮事；可是面對在前綫工作的好友Chris Hondros和Jim Foley相繼身亡，使Nicole對生命有更深刻的看法。其中Jim Foley被ISIS武裝份子擄走兩年後，被殺害的片段在全球發放，令她投身新聞工作的信念更為堅定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/humanitystories\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhumanitystories&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=e77f0cc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/humanitystories</a>"},{"pid":"865f00d6fb7d7549342827ea754fac7603cbc3ad","tid":2142855,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"睇到 sad sad 地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7a65ea3b3df4a935e4edc58bca99ebadab553a","tid":2142855,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796acfa3731bc020269fd3325d643104e24e1a73","tid":2142855,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"太heavy , 搵時間睇"},{"pid":"ad06618f490682ad9458b3e2f3fcfb246bd5171e","tid":2142855,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:30:44.000Z","msg":"【 《看見溫度》第二輯：生死過後 】<br />\n<br />\n童纓瑩（Nicole Tung）是一名攝影記者，多年來報道中東地區利比亞及敍利亞等地的戰火新聞。<br />\n<br />\n作為戰地記者，親眼目睹生離死別早已不是新鮮事；可是面對在前綫工作的好友Chris Hondros和Jim Foley相繼身亡，使Nicole對生命有更深刻的看法。其中Jim Foley被ISIS武裝份子擄走兩年後，被殺害的片段在全球發放，令她投身新聞工作的信念更為堅定。(導演：林亦非）<br />\n<br />\n後記：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3gDkuLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3gDkuLc&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=9d742a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3gDkuLc</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube全集：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bAQxEl85LmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbAQxEl85LmQ&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=fd8f0346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bAQxEl85LmQ</a><br />\n 港台網站:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/humanitystories/episode/694765\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhumanitystories%2Fepisode%2F694765&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=cf60b169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/humanitystories/episode/694765</a><br />\n<br />\n#生死過後 #看見溫度 <br />\n#香港電台 #電視部 #公共事務組<br />\n#外判紀錄片系列<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthkPCA/videos/2666270836978670/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FrthkPCA%2Fvideos%2F2666270836978670%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=e07bb59b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthkPCA/videos/2666270836978670/</a>"},{"pid":"3951e04f6576567b1e3254a460141c4d64c958ce","tid":2142855,"uid":121275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"《看見溫度：生死過後》拍攝手記<br />\n【文、圖： 林亦非 （攝影師、《生死過後》導演）】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/看見溫度-生死過後-拍攝手記/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%9C%8B%E8%A6%8B%E6%BA%AB%E5%BA%A6-%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C-%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E6%89%8B%E8%A8%98%2F&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=b7d02dae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%9C%8B%E8%A6%8B%E6%BA%AB%E5%BA%A6-%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8C-%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E6%89%8B%E8%A8%98%2F&h=03b95589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/看見溫度-生死過後-拍攝手記/</a>"},{"pid":"da0f873c933c409b15be09e8e4ace81b143c7971","tid":2142855,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/humanitystories/episode/694766\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhumanitystories%2Fepisode%2F694766&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOo2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=85f9c61d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/humanitystories/episode/694766</a><br />\n<br />\n許鴻文是梅嶺第三代的梅農。螢火蟲是他童年的玩伴，帶給他美好的回憶。可是，他讀國小的時候，梅農大肆使用農藥，從此螢火蟲就消聲匿跡。<br />\n<br />\n長大後，許鴻文成為梅嶺第一個有機梅農，他以一人之力把「童年的螢火蟲」復育回來........"},{"pid":"5a5c866515ed70c1313c352392b38bdd0c441107","tid":2142855,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"今集好睇, 有無人睇?"},{"pid":"47e64c97e45b2d67745ff4b4a5d84cab033b3804","tid":2142855,"uid":86449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"消失的冰川<br />\n位於青藏高原的阿尼瑪卿山，是世界最高的高原，被喻為「世界屋脊」，亦有第三極之稱。可是，在全球氣候變化中正面臨冰川消失危機，一個來自美國的年青攝影師Kyle Obermann，跟隨牧民，攀山涉水，探察著雪山的變化，在災難臨到之前，向世人發出警號!<br />\n